            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="26472868">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">人们常常说，民主政体就是以数人头的方式代替了砍人头的方式。</span>
                  &nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/26472868/">(<span class="">2回应</span>)</a>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2013-05-20 10:57</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                <blockquote><q>人们常常说，民主政体就是以数人头的方式代替了砍人头的方式。</q></blockquote>
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







<div class="rec-sec">

    <span class="rec">

